<h2><strong>Slogans ou Taglines</strong></h2>



<p>Primeiro, eu preciso fazer uma pequena observação. Os termos slogan e tagline são bem semelhantes, e por este motivo, são geralmente usados de forma intercambiável.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Porém, deve ser mencionado que há algumas pequenas diferenças entre um slogan e uma tagline.&nbsp;</p>



<p>O <a href="http://www.businessdictionary.com/definition/slogan.html" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">BusinessDictionary define um slogan</a> como “uma frase simples e memorável acompanhando uma logomarca ou uma marca que encapsula o apelo de um produto ou o propósito de uma firma e a torna mais memorável.”&nbsp;</p>



<p>“Há algumas coisas que o dinheiro não pode comprar. Para todas as outras, existe o MasterCard” é um bom exemplo.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="536" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-Mastercard.png" alt="1 Mastercard" class="wp-image-112906" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-Mastercard.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-Mastercard-300x157.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-Mastercard-768x402.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-Mastercard-380x199.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-Mastercard-600x314.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-Mastercard-760x398.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-Mastercard-67x35.png 67w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-Mastercard-96x50.png 96w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-Mastercard-740x387.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-Mastercard-220x115.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-Mastercard-385x202.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://penji.co/best-advertising-tactics/"></a></p>



<p>Por outro lado, <a href="https://www.thebalancesmb.com/what-is-a-tagline-4017760" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">The Balance Small Business</a> define uma tagline como “uma frase curta e memorável que é usada durante seu marketing. Ela deve transmitir o sentimento principal que você quer que as pessoas associem à sua marca.”</p>



<p>Considere o “Amo muito tudo isso” do McDonald’s, por exemplo.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="780" height="439" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-McDonalds.png" alt="2 McDonalds" class="wp-image-112910" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-McDonalds.png 780w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-McDonalds-300x169.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-McDonalds-768x432.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-McDonalds-380x214.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-McDonalds-600x338.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-McDonalds-760x428.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-McDonalds-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-McDonalds-89x50.png 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-McDonalds-740x416.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-McDonalds-220x124.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-McDonalds-385x217.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 780px) 100vw, 780px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.cbc.ca/radio/undertheinfluence/the-three-word-jingle-that-made-one-company-billions-of-dollars-1.4598645"></a></p>



<p>Então, uma das formas principais com a qual eles se diferenciam é com o comprimento, já que os slogans são geralmente mais compridos que as taglines.</p>



<p>Os slogans também tendem a ser um pouco mais concretos, focando no que a marca está vendendo e explicando por que aquilo é beneficial, enquanto as taglines tendem a ser mais abstratas e tentam passar um sentimento.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Embora hajam algumas pequenas diferenças, os dois possuem o mesmo objetivo—fazer com que a empresa seja mais identificável e ajudar os compradores a associar uma frase com sua marca.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Este é o seu objetivo final e é essencial para tornar um negócio reconhecível e desenvolver o valor de marca.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Além disso, há algumas outras grandes semelhanças entre os slogans e as taglines para o comércio eletrônico.&nbsp;</p>



<ul><li>Os dois são simples;</li><li>Os dois são memoráveis; e</li><li>Os dois passam sentimentos positivos para os compradores.</li></ul>



<h2><strong>12 dos melhores slogans e taglines para comércio eletrônico</strong></h2>



<p>Agora que esclarecemos isso, vamos aos detalhes.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Aqui está uma lista dos 12 melhores slogans e taglines para comércio eletrônico de algumas das maiores marcas de hoje, além de algumas observações sobre o que os torna tão eficazes.&nbsp;</p>



<h2><strong>1. Allbirds: “Os sapatos mais confortáveis do mundo”</strong></h2>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="491" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3-Allbirds-1024x491.png" alt="3 Allbirds" class="wp-image-112914" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3-Allbirds-1024x491.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3-Allbirds-300x144.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3-Allbirds-768x368.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3-Allbirds-1536x736.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3-Allbirds-380x182.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3-Allbirds-600x288.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3-Allbirds-760x364.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3-Allbirds-1440x690.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3-Allbirds-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3-Allbirds-104x50.png 104w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3-Allbirds-740x355.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3-Allbirds-220x105.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3-Allbirds-385x185.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3-Allbirds.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.allbirds.com/"><strong></strong></a></p>



<p><a href="https://www.allbirds.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Allbirds</a> é uma de minhas marcas de calçados favoritas e uma empresa que realmente “entende das coisas.”</p>



<p>A marca usa materiais naturais para produzir seus sapatos e põe uma forte ênfase em ser uma empresa ecológica.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="383" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Allbirds-Sponge-1024x383.png" alt="4 Allbirds Sponge" class="wp-image-112918" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Allbirds-Sponge-1024x383.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Allbirds-Sponge-300x112.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Allbirds-Sponge-768x287.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Allbirds-Sponge-1536x574.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Allbirds-Sponge-380x142.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Allbirds-Sponge-600x224.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Allbirds-Sponge-760x284.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Allbirds-Sponge-1440x538.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Allbirds-Sponge-94x35.png 94w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Allbirds-Sponge-134x50.png 134w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Allbirds-Sponge-740x277.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Allbirds-Sponge-220x82.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Allbirds-Sponge-385x144.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Allbirds-Sponge.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.allbirds.com/pages/our-materials-wool"></a></p>



<p>Além disso, seus sapatos são bastante confortáveis. Então, que melhor slogan usar do que “Os sapatos mais confortáveis de mundo?”</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="506" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Allbirds-Shoes-1024x506.png" alt="5 Allbirds Shoes" class="wp-image-112922" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Allbirds-Shoes-1024x506.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Allbirds-Shoes-300x148.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Allbirds-Shoes-768x380.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Allbirds-Shoes-1536x759.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Allbirds-Shoes-380x188.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Allbirds-Shoes-600x297.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Allbirds-Shoes-760x376.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Allbirds-Shoes-1440x712.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Allbirds-Shoes-71x35.png 71w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Allbirds-Shoes-101x50.png 101w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Allbirds-Shoes-740x366.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Allbirds-Shoes-220x109.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Allbirds-Shoes-385x190.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Allbirds-Shoes.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Este slogan acerta em tudo. É simples, memorável, ajuda a diferenciar o Allbirds de seus competidores e passa sentimentos positivos.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>



<p>Além disso, ele captura instantaneamente o interesse de vários compradores. Eu não sei você, mas o conforto é algo extremamente importante para mim quando estou escolhendo um par de sapatos.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Eu sou atraído instantaneamente por uma marca que promete oferecer os sapatos mais confortáveis do mundo. Por isso, podemos aprender bastante com este exemplo.&nbsp;</p>



<h2><strong>2. Two Chimps Coffee: “Café incrível. Sem enrolação.”</strong></h2>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="474" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Two-Chimps-1024x474.png" alt="6 Two Chimps" class="wp-image-112926" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Two-Chimps-1024x474.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Two-Chimps-300x139.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Two-Chimps-768x355.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Two-Chimps-1536x711.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Two-Chimps-380x176.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Two-Chimps-600x278.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Two-Chimps-760x352.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Two-Chimps-1440x666.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Two-Chimps-76x35.png 76w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Two-Chimps-108x50.png 108w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Two-Chimps-740x342.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Two-Chimps-220x102.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Two-Chimps-385x178.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Two-Chimps.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://twochimpscoffee.com/"></a></p>



<p>Aqui está uma marca com assinatura de venda de café com produtos recém-torrados e produzidos de origens éticas.&nbsp;</p>



<p>A marca chamou muita atenção recentemente por seu café de alta qualidade e marketing inteligente.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="498" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Two-chimps-Coffee-1024x498.png" alt="7 Two chimps Coffee" class="wp-image-112930" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Two-chimps-Coffee-1024x498.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Two-chimps-Coffee-300x146.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Two-chimps-Coffee-768x374.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Two-chimps-Coffee-1536x748.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Two-chimps-Coffee-380x185.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Two-chimps-Coffee-600x292.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Two-chimps-Coffee-760x370.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Two-chimps-Coffee-1440x701.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Two-chimps-Coffee-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Two-chimps-Coffee-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Two-chimps-Coffee-740x360.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Two-chimps-Coffee-220x107.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Two-chimps-Coffee-385x187.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Two-chimps-Coffee.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://twochimpscoffee.com/"></a></p>



<p>E grande parte desse sucesso vem de seu slogan “Café incrível. Sem enrolação.” Com apenas quatro palavras, o <a href="https://twochimpscoffee.com/">Two Chimps Coffee</a> encapsula perfeitamente o que está vendendo e se estabelece como algo que vale a pena comprar.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Também ajuda que a marca é sem enrolação, isso quer dizer que os compradores não precisam se preocupar em ter algum problema ou conflito ao lidar com o Two Chimps Coffee.</p>



<p>Em vez disso, eles podem esperar ter uma experiência profissional e agradável.&nbsp;</p>



<h2><strong>3. Bonobos: “Roupas masculinas que servem, feitas com bom serviço e focadas em estilo. Sirva-se como quiser, o Bonobos serve em você.”</strong></h2>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="501" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Bonobos-1024x501.png" alt="8 Bonobos" class="wp-image-112934" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Bonobos-1024x501.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Bonobos-300x147.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Bonobos-768x376.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Bonobos-1536x752.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Bonobos-380x186.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Bonobos-600x294.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Bonobos-760x372.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Bonobos-1440x705.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Bonobos-71x35.png 71w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Bonobos-102x50.png 102w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Bonobos-740x362.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Bonobos-220x108.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Bonobos-385x189.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Bonobos.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://bonobos.com/"><strong></strong></a></p>



<p>Este é certamente um dos slogans mais compridos, alcançando 20 palavras.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Mas o <a href="https://bonobos.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Bonobos</a> faz um ótimo trabalho resumindo o que vende (roupas masculinas), o que ele valoriza (um ótimo estilo) e por que vale a pena fazer negócio com sua marca (ele tem produtos fantásticos e um excelente serviço ao cliente).</p>



<p>Como resultado, ele foi capaz de atrair um público e gerar um interesse inicial bem forte.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Assim que os compradores visitam o site da marca, eles podem perceber instantaneamente que o Bonobos é super profissional com uma coleção extensa de produtos masculinos criativos como estes shorts e camisetas com tons pastéis.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="493" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Bonobos-shirts-1024x493.png" alt="8 Bonobos" class="wp-image-112938" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Bonobos-shirts-1024x493.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Bonobos-shirts-300x145.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Bonobos-shirts-768x370.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Bonobos-shirts-1536x740.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Bonobos-shirts-380x183.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Bonobos-shirts-600x289.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Bonobos-shirts-760x366.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Bonobos-shirts-1440x694.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Bonobos-shirts-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Bonobos-shirts-104x50.png 104w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Bonobos-shirts-740x356.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Bonobos-shirts-220x106.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Bonobos-shirts-385x185.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Bonobos-shirts.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://bonobos.com/"></a></p>



<p>Basta começar com o pé direito com seu slogan ou tagline e convencer os seus compradores em potencial a darem uma chance para a sua marca.&nbsp;</p>



<h2><strong>4. Lunya: “Roupas de dormir para a mulher moderna”</strong></h2>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="487" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Lunya-1024x487.png" alt="10 Lunya" class="wp-image-112942" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Lunya-1024x487.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Lunya-300x143.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Lunya-768x365.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Lunya-1536x730.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Lunya-380x181.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Lunya-600x285.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Lunya-760x361.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Lunya-1440x684.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Lunya-74x35.png 74w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Lunya-105x50.png 105w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Lunya-740x352.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Lunya-220x105.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Lunya-385x183.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Lunya.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.lunya.co/"><strong></strong></a></p>



<p>Assim como o Allbirds e o Two Chimps Coffee, a <a href="https://www.lunya.co/">Lunya</a> explica de forma bastante breve o que está vendendo em apenas algumas palavras.&nbsp;</p>



<p>E considerando que seus produtos são feitos especificamente para metade da população (mulheres), ela fez um trabalho fantástico implementando isso em seu slogan de comércio eletrônico.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Isto garante que a Lunya chame o interesse de seu demográfico alvo e possa atrair os compradores certos.</p>



<p>Assim que visitarem o site da Lunya, os produtos combinam com seu slogan de comércio eletrônico e os compradores podem navegar por uma boa seleção de roupões, pijamas, máscaras de dormir, entre outros.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="474" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Lunya-Sleepwear-1024x474.png" alt="11 Lunya Sleepwear" class="wp-image-112946" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Lunya-Sleepwear-1024x474.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Lunya-Sleepwear-300x139.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Lunya-Sleepwear-768x356.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Lunya-Sleepwear-1536x712.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Lunya-Sleepwear-380x176.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Lunya-Sleepwear-600x278.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Lunya-Sleepwear-760x352.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Lunya-Sleepwear-1440x667.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Lunya-Sleepwear-76x35.png 76w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Lunya-Sleepwear-108x50.png 108w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Lunya-Sleepwear-740x343.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Lunya-Sleepwear-220x102.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Lunya-Sleepwear-385x178.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Lunya-Sleepwear.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.lunya.co/"></a></p>



<p>Por isso, quando se trata de simplicidade e de ser super direto, este slogan com certeza acerta em cheio.&nbsp;</p>



<h2><strong>5. Birchbox: “Caixas de Produtos de Beleza e Cuidados Pessoais Mensais”</strong></h2>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="498" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Birchbox-1024x498.png" alt="12 Birchbox" class="wp-image-112950" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Birchbox-1024x498.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Birchbox-300x146.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Birchbox-768x374.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Birchbox-1536x748.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Birchbox-380x185.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Birchbox-600x292.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Birchbox-760x370.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Birchbox-1440x701.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Birchbox-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Birchbox-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Birchbox-740x360.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Birchbox-220x107.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Birchbox-385x187.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Birchbox.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.birchbox.com/"><strong></strong></a></p>



<p><a href="https://www.birchbox.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Birchbox</a> é um dos maiores serviços de assinatura online para produtos de maquiagem, cuidados de pele e de cabelo.&nbsp;</p>



<p>A marca criou uma base de seguidores fiéis, em grande parte devido à sua transparência e ao processo de compra simplificado que oferece aos seus consumidores.&nbsp;</p>



<p>O slogan de comércio eletrônico, “Caixas de Produtos de Beleza e Cuidados Pessoais Mensais,” é bem direto e rapidamente deixa que os compradores saibam o que o Birchbox está oferecendo.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Após visitar o seu site, o Birchbox oferece uma explicação rápida de como o processo funciona, deixando que os compradores saibam o que esperar quando adquirirem uma assinatura de caixas mensais.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="567" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Birchbox-Order-1024x567.png" alt="13 Birchbox Order" class="wp-image-112954" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Birchbox-Order-1024x567.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Birchbox-Order-300x166.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Birchbox-Order-768x425.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Birchbox-Order-1536x850.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Birchbox-Order-380x210.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Birchbox-Order-600x332.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Birchbox-Order-760x420.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Birchbox-Order-1440x797.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Birchbox-Order-63x35.png 63w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Birchbox-Order-90x50.png 90w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Birchbox-Order-740x409.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Birchbox-Order-220x122.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Birchbox-Order-385x213.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Birchbox-Order.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.birchbox.com/"></a></p>



<p>Mais uma vez, este exemplo demonstra que os melhores slogans e taglines para comércio eletrônico são simples, remetendo as informações principais que os clientes em potencial precisam saber de forma concisa.&nbsp;</p>



<h2><strong>6. Flat Tummy Co: “Purificação e detox ou corte de calorias”</strong></h2>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="506" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Flat-Tummy--1024x506.png" alt="14 Flat Tummy" class="wp-image-112958" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Flat-Tummy--1024x506.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Flat-Tummy--300x148.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Flat-Tummy--768x380.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Flat-Tummy--1536x759.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Flat-Tummy--380x188.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Flat-Tummy--600x297.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Flat-Tummy--760x376.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Flat-Tummy--1440x712.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Flat-Tummy--71x35.png 71w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Flat-Tummy--101x50.png 101w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Flat-Tummy--740x366.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Flat-Tummy--220x109.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Flat-Tummy--385x190.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Flat-Tummy-.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://flattummyco.com/"></a></p>



<p>Aqui está uma marca de comércio eletrônico que se especializa em produtos de controle de peso para mulheres, como bebidas, chás e pirulitos, além de roupas e tapetes de exercício.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Dado que a marca possui atualmente 1,7 milhões de seguidores no Instagram, ela fez um ótimo trabalhando se conectado com seu público alvo e criando uma forte comunidade digital.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="557" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-1024x557.png" alt="15 $flat Tummy Insta" class="wp-image-112962" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-1024x557.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-300x163.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-768x418.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-1536x835.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-380x207.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-600x326.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-760x413.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-1440x783.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-64x35.png 64w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-92x50.png 92w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-740x402.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-220x120.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-385x209.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/flattummyco/"></a></p>



<p>Como mencionei antes, um primeiro passo crítico para chegar a este nível é criar um slogan ou tagline de comércio eletrônico que comunica do que sua marca se trata.&nbsp;</p>



<p>O <a href="https://flattummyco.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Flat Tummy Co</a> consegue fazer isso perfeitamente tendo “Purificação e detox ou corte de calorias” como seu slogan.</p>



<p>Com apenas algumas palavras, os clientes em potencial sabem o que podem esperar conseguir comprando os produtos do Flat Tummy Co’s, que chamam a atenção de seu público alvo.&nbsp;</p>



<h2><strong>7. Everlane: “O básico moderno. Transparência radical.”</strong></h2>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="455" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-1024x455.png" alt="16 Everlane" class="wp-image-112966" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-1024x455.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-300x133.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-768x342.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-1536x683.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-380x169.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-600x267.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-760x338.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-1440x640.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-79x35.png 79w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-112x50.png 112w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-740x329.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-220x98.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-385x171.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.everlane.com/"><strong></strong></a></p>



<p><a href="https://www.everlane.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Everlane</a> é uma loja de roupas online que chamou muita atenção com o passar dos anos. A marca ganhou uma ótima reputação, e atualmente, está chegando a um milhão de seguidores no Instagram.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="596" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-1024x596.png" alt="17 Everlane Insta" class="wp-image-112970" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-1024x596.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-300x175.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-768x447.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-1536x894.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-380x221.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-600x349.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-760x443.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-1440x838.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-60x35.png 60w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-86x50.png 86w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-740x431.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-220x128.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-385x224.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/everlane/"></a></p>



<p>O Everlane acertou em várias coisas, e seu slogan de comércio eletrônico faz um trabalho excelente comunicando do que sua marca se trata—de oferecer roupas básicas e minimalistas, enquanto sendo completamente transparente sobre seus valores.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Para ser claro, seus valores são criar roupas utilizando materiais sustentáveis, que também são produzidos de origens éticas.&nbsp;</p>



<h2><strong>8. Girlfriend Collective: “Roupas de exercício éticas”</strong></h2>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="478" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-1024x478.png" alt="18 GF Collective" class="wp-image-112974" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-1024x478.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-300x140.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-768x358.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-1536x717.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-380x177.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-600x280.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-760x355.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-1440x672.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-75x35.png 75w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-107x50.png 107w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-740x345.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-220x103.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-385x180.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.girlfriend.com/"></a></p>



<p>Esta é uma marca que cria roupas de exercício de materiais 100 por cento reciclados.</p>



<p>Em seu site, você encontrará uma frase engraçada e humorística que diz, “A Girlfriend Collective cria roupas de exercício de materiais reciclados, porque lixo é mais bonito em você do que poluindo o planeta.”</p>



<p>E seu slogan está alinhado perfeitamente com sua <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-value-proposition" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">proposição de valor</a> usando apenas três palavras—“Roupas de exercício éticas.”</p>



<p>Isto imediatamente deixa os clientes em potencial saberem do que a <a href="https://www.girlfriend.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Girlfriend Collective</a> se trata e prova que é possível resumir o propósito, os valores e a filosofia de sua marca em um slogan ultra simples.&nbsp;</p>



<h2><strong>9. Primary Clothing: “O básico incrível para bebês e crianças”</strong></h2>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="470" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-1024x470.png" alt="19 Primary" class="wp-image-112978" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-1024x470.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-300x138.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-768x352.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-1536x705.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-380x174.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-600x275.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-760x349.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-1440x661.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-76x35.png 76w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-109x50.png 109w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-740x339.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-220x101.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-385x177.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.primary.com/"></a></p>



<p>Aqui temos outra empresa que usa a palavra “básico” em seu slogan.&nbsp;</p>



<p><a href="https://www.primary.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Primary Clothing</a> é uma marca que foca em oferecer “roupas para crianças de qualidade inesperada por uma fração do preço.” Ao ler seu slogan, os compradores sabem que a Primary Clothing foca especificamente em crianças.</p>



<p>E por utilizar as palavras “o básico incrível,” os compradores sabem que podem encontrar um alto nível de qualidade, ajudando a Primary Clothing a se diferenciar de competidores semelhantes no mercado.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Isto é algo que a marca reforça em seu site, onde ela explica exatamente o que a torna tão boa.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="470" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-1024x470.png" alt="20 Primary Rainbow" class="wp-image-112982" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-1024x470.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-300x138.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-768x352.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-1536x705.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-380x174.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-600x275.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-760x349.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-1440x661.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-76x35.png 76w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-109x50.png 109w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-740x339.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-220x101.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-385x177.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<h2><strong>10. Sephora: “Vamos ser lindos juntos”</strong></h2>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="476" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-1024x476.png" alt="21 Sephora" class="wp-image-112986" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-1024x476.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-300x140.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-768x357.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-1536x715.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-380x177.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-600x279.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-760x354.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-1440x670.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-75x35.png 75w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-107x50.png 107w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-740x344.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-220x102.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-385x179.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Em meus exemplos finais, eu irei dar exemplos de marcas com ótimas taglines. Como eu disse antes, as taglines tendem a ser um pouco mais abstratas do que os slogans e tentam passar uma imagem às mentes dos compradores.&nbsp;</p>



<p>No final das contas, as taglines se tratam principalmente de ajudar os compradores a formarem associações entre uma certa frase e uma marca—considere a tagline da Nike, “Apenas faça.”</p>



<p>Sendo assim, é mais comum ver empresas maiores e mais estabelecidas usando taglines, porque elas já possuem uma certa quantidade de valor de marca.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Um dos melhores exemplos é a tagline da Sephora, “Vamos ser lindos juntos.” Isto claramente diz aos compradores que a marca se trata de vender produtos de beleza e é uma forma criativa de transmitir sua atitude amigável.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>



<p>E com apenas quatro palavras, é uma frase curta, linda e memorável.&nbsp;</p>



<h2><strong>11. TOMS: “Nosso negócio é melhorar vidas”</strong></h2>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="498" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-1024x498.png" alt="22 TOMS" class="wp-image-112990" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-1024x498.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-300x146.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-768x374.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-1536x748.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-380x185.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-600x292.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-760x370.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-1440x701.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-740x360.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-220x107.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-385x187.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.toms.com/"></a></p>



<p><a href="https://www.toms.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">TOMS</a> é um dos criadores do modelo de negócios “one-for-one” onde para cada par de sapatos comprados, eles dão de presente um par de sapatos para alguém que precisa.</p>



<p>Na medida em que a marca cresceu com o passar dos anos, ela melhorou seu modelo ligeiramente, mas sua identidade de marca continua sendo extremamente focada em ajudar as pessoas do mundo e em avançar o progresso.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Usar a tagline, “Nosso negócio é melhorar vidas,” é perfeito para articular os valores da TOMS e demonstrar que a mudança positiva é a força que move sua empresa.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Isto deveria ser o bastante para capturar o interesse de várias pessoas e levá-las direto ao site da TOMS. A partir daí, os compradores podem saber mais sobre seu propósito e ver seus produtos.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="496" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image-32-1024x496.png" alt="" class="wp-image-113074" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image-32-1024x496.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image-32-300x145.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image-32-768x372.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image-32-1536x744.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image-32-380x184.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image-32-600x291.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image-32-760x368.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image-32-1440x698.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image-32-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image-32-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image-32-740x358.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image-32-220x107.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image-32-385x186.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image-32.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.toms.com/"></a></p>



<p>E isto é algo que você pode usar como inspiração para implementar em sua marca de comércio eletrônico.&nbsp;</p>



<h2><strong>12. Chubbies: “O fim-de-semana chegou”</strong></h2>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="497" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-1024x497.png" alt="24 Chubbies" class="wp-image-112998" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-1024x497.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-300x146.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-768x373.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-1536x745.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-380x184.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-600x291.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-760x369.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-1440x699.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-740x359.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-220x107.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-385x187.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.chubbiesshorts.com/"></a></p>



<p>Por fim, temos o <a href="https://www.chubbiesshorts.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Chubbies</a>, uma das marcas de roupas masculinas mais humorísticas e modernas que existem.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Para falar a verdade, “O fim-de-semana chegou” é uma das taglines de comércio eletrônico mais vagas que existem. E se você já não estivesse familiarizado com o Chubbies, é provável que você nem soubesse o que esperar dele.</p>



<p>É por isso que esta não é necessariamente a melhor rota a se seguir se você é uma pequena empresa que está tentando conseguir uma base de clientes e seguidores fiéis.</p>



<p>Mas se você já possui um público considerável e está procurando fortalecer sua identidade de marca, esta rota certamente pode fazer sentido.</p>



<p>No caso do Chubbies’, usar a frase “O fim-de-semana chegou” transmite sentimentos de diversão e alegria, algo que certamente se alinha com sua identidade de marca.</p>



<p>Dê uma olhada em alguns dos produtos legais que ele vende, como esses calções de banho masculinos.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="509" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-1024x509.png" alt="25 Chubbies Shorts" class="wp-image-113002" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-1024x509.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-300x149.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-768x382.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-1536x764.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-380x189.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-600x298.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-760x378.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-1440x716.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-70x35.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-101x50.png 101w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-740x368.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-220x109.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-385x191.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.chubbiesshorts.com/collections/best-sellers#daily-hot-deals"></a></p>



<p>E dê uma olhada em algumas das publicações hilárias em sua página do Instagram.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="636" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-1024x636.png" alt="26 Chubbies Insta" class="wp-image-113006" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-1024x636.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-300x186.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-768x477.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-1536x954.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-380x236.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-600x372.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-760x472.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-1440x894.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-81x50.png 81w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-740x459.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-220x137.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-385x239.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/chubbies/?hl=en"></a></p>



<p>O ponto onde estou querendo chegar é que para criar uma tagline incrível, é preciso um pouco de sutileza e um certo nível de relação com um público existente.</p>



<p>Mas o Chubbies é a prova de que isso pode ser feito se você utilizar a fórmula certa.&nbsp;</p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5fa9462cf97aa" class="block-content-upgrade">
    <div class="text">
        <p class="text-pretitle">RECURSOS GRATUITOS</p>
        <h2 class="text-title">Precisa de mais inspiração para seu copywriting?</h2>
        <div class="text-content"><p>Tenha acesso a nosso swipe file repleto de exemplos de call-to-action, modelos de e-mail, páginas de comércio eletrônico de alto desempenho e muito mais.</p>
</div>
                    <a onClick="SleekNote.triggerOnclick('00c91b9b-1dbc-48da-8d77-1dd2cfc8355b');" href="javascript:void(0);" class="text-link" title="Baixar swipe file agora →">Baixar swipe file agora →</a>
            </div>
    <div class="image">
        <img src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Grow-Your-Email-List@2x-1.png" title="Precisa de mais inspiração para seu copywriting?">    </div>
</div>


<h2><strong>Conclusão</strong></h2>



<p>Criar um slogan ou tagline para um comércio eletrônico é uma parte crítica para estabelecer sua identidade de marca e direcionar seu público alvo à sua loja.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Slogans e taglines são um pouco diferentes, mas possuem o mesmo objetivo de fazer com que sua marca seja reconhecível, além de desenvolver o valor de marca.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Algumas coisas que os melhores slogans e taglines têm em comum é que eles são simples, memoráveis e passam sentimentos positivos para os compradores. E em alguns casos, eles mencionam uma vantagem específica por escolher uma certa marca.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Os exemplos apresentados aqui são alguns dos melhores slogans e taglines para comércio eletrônico que eu encontrei e demonstram como realizar o processo. Espero que tenham dado a você um pouco de inspiração para que você possa criar seu próprio slogan ou tagline.&nbsp;</p>



<p><em>Quais destes exemplos você gostou mais e por quê?</em></p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://sleeknote.com/pt-pt/blog/melhores-slogans-comercio-eletronico">12 dos melhores slogans e taglines para comércio eletrônico</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://sleeknote.com/pt-pt">Sleeknote</a>.</p>
