<p>E até mesmo idade.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="428" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Percent-of-Optimal-Subscribers_-Send-Times-by-Hour-of-Day-2-1024x428.png" alt="Percent of Optimal Subscribers_ Send Times by Hour of Day 2" class="wp-image-91047" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Percent-of-Optimal-Subscribers_-Send-Times-by-Hour-of-Day-2-1024x428.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Percent-of-Optimal-Subscribers_-Send-Times-by-Hour-of-Day-2-300x125.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Percent-of-Optimal-Subscribers_-Send-Times-by-Hour-of-Day-2-768x321.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Percent-of-Optimal-Subscribers_-Send-Times-by-Hour-of-Day-2-380x159.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Percent-of-Optimal-Subscribers_-Send-Times-by-Hour-of-Day-2-600x251.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Percent-of-Optimal-Subscribers_-Send-Times-by-Hour-of-Day-2-760x318.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Percent-of-Optimal-Subscribers_-Send-Times-by-Hour-of-Day-2-84x35.png 84w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Percent-of-Optimal-Subscribers_-Send-Times-by-Hour-of-Day-2-120x50.png 120w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Percent-of-Optimal-Subscribers_-Send-Times-by-Hour-of-Day-2-740x309.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Percent-of-Optimal-Subscribers_-Send-Times-by-Hour-of-Day-2-220x92.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-