										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>É por isso que os seus emails acabam no Spam (e o que fazer a respeito)</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/pt-pt/blog/category/sem-categoria" rel="category tag">Sem categoria</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Why-Emails-Go-to-Spam-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg" alt="Why Emails Go to Spam (WordPress)" class="wp-image-90856" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Why-Emails-Go-to-Spam-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Why-Emails-Go-to-Spam-Wordpress-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Why-Emails-Go-to-Spam-Wordpress-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Why-Emails-Go-to-Spam-Wordpress-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Why-Emails-Go-to-Spam-Wordpress-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Why-Emails-Go-to-Spam-Wordpress-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Why-Emails-Go-to-Spam-Wordpress-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Why-Emails-Go-to-Spam-Wordpress-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Why-Emails-Go-to-Spam-Wordpress-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Why-Emails-Go-to-Spam-Wordpress-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Why-Emails-Go-to-Spam-Wordpress-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Why-Emails-Go-to-Spam-Wordpress-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Why-Emails-Go-to-Spam-Wordpress-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Why-Emails-Go-to-Spam-Wordpress-385x164.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Why-Emails-Go-to-Spam-Wordpress.jpg 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_5e98298d880f3" class="block-preamble"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">O e-mail foi e continua sendo um recurso inestimável para os profissionais de marketing.</span></p>
</div>






<p>Uma pesquisa da Direct Marketing Association e da Demand Metric revelou: &#8220;O email teve um <a href="https://www.emarketer.com/Article/Email-Continues-Deliver-Strong-ROI-Value-Marketers/1014461" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">ROI (<em>Return of Investment</em>, ou retorno de investimento) médio de 122%</a> &#8211; mais de quatro vezes maior que diversos formatos de marketing, incluindo mídia social, mala direta e pesquisa paga&#8221;.</p>



<p>Então, ele definitivamente funciona.</p>



<p>Mas há um problema que todos os profissionais de marketing de e-mail enfrentam eventualmente: o temido buraco negro do esquecimento que é a pasta de spam.</p>



<p>O Relatório de Referência de Entregabilidade de 2017 da Return Path descobriu que <a href="https://returnpath.com/downloads/2017-deliverability-benchmark-report/?sfdc=70137000000EUhC" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">20% de todos os emails comerciais</a> acabam sendo identificados como spam.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="530" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Return-Path’s-2017-Deliverability-Benchmark-Report-1024x530.png" alt="Return Path’s 2017 Deliverability Benchmark Report" class="wp-image-90844" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Return-Path’s-2017-Deliverability-Benchmark-Report-1024x530.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Return-Path’s-2017-Deliverability-Benchmark-Report-300x155.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Return-Path’s-2017-Deliverability-Benchmark-Report-768x398.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Return-Path’s-2017-Deliverability-Benchmark-Report-380x197.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Return-Path’s-2017-Deliverability-Benchmark-Report-600x311.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Return-Path’s-2017-Deliverability-Benchmark-Report-760x394.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Return-Path’s-2017-Deliverability-Benchmark-Report-68x35.png 68w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Return-Path’s-2017-Deliverability-Benchmark-Report-97x50.png 97w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Return-Path’s-2017-Deliverability-Benchmark-Report-740x383.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Return-Path’s-2017-Deliverability-Benchmark-Report-220x114.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Return-Path’s-2017-Deliverability-Benchmark-Report-385x199.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Return-Path’s-2017-Deliverability-Benchmark-Report.png 1058w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>E sejamos francos. Uma vez ali, um e-mail é praticamente um caso perdido.</p>



<p>Quantas pessoas realmente gastam tempo vasculhando a sua pasta de spam para ver se, talvez, apenas seu e-mail tenha sido enviado equivocadamente para lá?</p>



<p>Meu palpite seria <em>ninguém</em>.</p>



<p>E isso é um problema, porque a taxa média de abertura é de <a href="https://blog.hubspot.com/sales/average-email-open-rate-benchmark" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">apenas 32%</a>, e chega a ser ainda menor para certos setores.</p>



<p>Portanto, quando você leva em conta os emails enviados para spam, esse número diminui ainda mais.</p>



<p>No momento, discutirei alguns motivos comuns pelos quais os emails são enviados para a caixa de spam, e como evitar que os seus fiquem presos lá.</p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5e982a30880f4" class="block-content-upgrade">
    <div class="text">
        <p class="text-pretitle">RECURSOS GRATUITOS</p>
        <h2 class="text-title">Quer mais inspiração de marketing por e-mail?</h2>
        <div class="text-content"><p>Reunimos um arquivo de 41 exemplos de e-mail de comércio eletrônico, 115 a partir de linhas de assunto e mais, para ajudar você a gerar mais aberturas, cliques e conversões para suas campanhas de marketing hoje (organizadas por categoria).</p>
</div>
                    <a onClick="SleekNote.triggerOnclick('00c91b9b-1dbc-48da-8d77-1dd2cfc8355b');" href="javascript:void(0);" class="text-link" title="Baixe o Bônus Gratuito Hoje Mesmo →">Baixe o Bônus Gratuito Hoje Mesmo →</a>
