<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>Como criar anúncios de Lead incríveis e com alta conversão para o facebook</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/pt-pt/blog/category/sem-categoria" rel="category tag">Sem categoria</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Facebook-Lead-Ads-Wordpress-1-1024x437.jpg" alt="Facebook Lead Ads (WordPress)" class="wp-image-91591" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Facebook-Lead-Ads-Wordpress-1-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Facebook-Lead-Ads-Wordpress-1-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Facebook-Lead-Ads-Wordpress-1-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Facebook-Lead-Ads-Wordpress-1-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Facebook-Lead-Ads-Wordpress-1-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Facebook-Lead-Ads-Wordpress-1-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Facebook-Lead-Ads-Wordpress-1-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Facebook-Lead-Ads-Wordpress-1-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Facebook-Lead-Ads-Wordpress-1-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Facebook-Lead-Ads-Wordpress-1-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Facebook-Lead-Ads-Wordpress-1-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Facebook-Lead-Ads-Wordpress-1-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Facebook-Lead-Ads-Wordpress-1-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wp